{"tid":522954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劏房閣樓傳出臭味 揭發男子倒斃多日","createTime":"2018-01-08T04:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T05:00:28.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dde231af26354daa955d85c57b6de7de6b284e46","tid":522954,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"觀塘雲漢街63號地下一個劏房閣樓，早上10時許，鄰居嗅到大陣異味，報警求助，警員到場調查，揭發閣樓一名56歲男住客倒卧閣樓床上，救護員證實事主已當場死亡，屍身滲出血水，相信已死去一段時間。警員稍後聯絡死者友人了解事件，獲知死者無業，仍調查死者是否有長期病患，事件並無可疑，死因有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180108/57680099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57680099&d=n2QiVH5lzydu35rodligO%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6a0954d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57680099&h=2f72b094\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180108/57680099</a>"},{"pid":"24ee401a361805d0162d5640cbec4e7dc26fc3ba","tid":522954,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"未來的我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}